name: Monolith
description: Remaining calm in the storm. A special OBJKT created to celebrate my 30.000th tweet and more than 12 years on Twitter. So much has happened in the meanwhile, good, bad, but I'm happy and grateful for how far I've come. Thank you to the HEN community. (15s loop + sound - 1080x1080 - 60fps - created by @ufunk_parse)
